Class StringMenuOwner<T>

    • org.jemmy.input.StringCriteriaList<T>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ControlInterface, MenuOwner<T>, TypeControlInterface<T>

    public abstract class StringMenuOwner<T>
extends StringCriteriaList<T>
implements MenuOwner<T>
    In most cases menu has a text associated with every menu item. This interface makes it easy to push the menu based on that text information.

    shura
